original_title: レイプハンター開発計画 File_07 美少女仮面オーロラ-Three- VS 新レイプハンター 通野未帆
overview: The rape hunter Biff appears in front of the beautiful masked girl Aurora who protects the safety and peace of the city! The rape hunter rips the sacred suit with an electromagnetic whip and launches an attack that leaves no room for embarrassment. She was transformed by the power of light, and although she was strong, she was sealed in the venom of the universe! Goddess Sedna gives her all her powers and makes Aurora her Sun Warrior. Aurora, who has become the strongest goddess, turns around, but she shows a gap in her life and is killed. The goddess Sedna possesses the corpse of Aurora and tries to defeat the rape hunter, but everything was a plan to capture the goddess Sedna alive! [BAD END]
title: A Development Project of RapeHunter File 07:Pretty Kamen Aurora -Three- VS New Rape Hunter Tsuno Miho
